{
  "texts": [
    "The primary objective is to assess healthcare chatbot models from the perspective of users interacting with the healthcare chatbot, thereby distinguishing our approach from existing studies in this field.",
    "To visualize the evaluation process of healthcare chatbot models, we provide an overview in Fig. 2.",
    "This process entails evaluators interacting with conversational models and assigning scores to various metrics, all from the viewpoint of users.",
    "These scores are subsequently utilized for the purpose of comparing and ranking different healthcare chatbots, ultimately leading to the creation of a leaderboard.",
    "In this evaluation process, three confounding variables are taken into account: user type, domain type, and task type."
  ]
}